DESCRIPTION: This React functional component (MainPage.jsx) demonstrates how to use Wasp's generated CRUD operations on the client. It imports `Tasks` from `wasp/client/crud`, fetches all tasks using `Tasks.getAll.useQuery()`, and provides functionality to create new tasks using `Tasks.create.useAction()`. It handles loading and error states and renders a list of tasks and an input form.
