TITLE: Implementing updateTask Action Server Logic in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: Provides the TypeScript server-side implementation for the `updateTask` action. It utilizes Wasp's generated types (`UpdateTask`, `Task`) for type safety. The function accepts an object with `id` and `isDone` (typed using `UpdateTaskPayload`, derived from the `Task` entity) and the Wasp `context`. It updates the task in the database using `context.entities.Task.update`.
