TITLE: Defining a Todo List React Component Using API Calls and Type Annotations - TypeScript (TSX)
DESCRIPTION: Implements a typed Todo component that fetches a list of Task objects from an API endpoint using the wasp/client/api client. Utilizes useState and useEffect, ensuring type safety for both state and API response. Suitable for integration testing where API responses must be controlled.
