TITLE: Creating a React Component Using Wasp Queries (JSX)
DESCRIPTION: Defines a React component `Todo` in JSX (`src/Todo.jsx`). This component uses the `useQuery` hook from `wasp/client/operations` to fetch tasks via the `getTasks` query and renders them as a list.
