TITLE: Implementing a Custom Root React Component (JavaScript, JSX)
DESCRIPTION: This custom React component serves as the application's root when using JavaScript, providing global context via a Redux Provider and rendering a custom layout. Required dependencies are 'react-redux' and the application's store module. The 'Root' component expects children and wraps them with the Layout structure, providing header and footer sections. Inputs: children (React nodes); Output: wrapped application. Limitations: Provider and Layout structure must match application requirements.
