TITLE: JavaScript Database Seed Implementation
DESCRIPTION: Implementation of a database seed function in JavaScript, creating initial user and task data.
SOURCE: https://github.com/wasp-lang/wasp/blob/main/web/versioned_docs/version-0.15.0/data-model/backends.md#2025-04-22_snippet_4

