TITLE: Implementing Authenticated Task Operations
DESCRIPTION: Implements createTask and updateTask actions with authentication checks and user-specific data access. Includes both JavaScript and TypeScript implementations.
SOURCE: https://github.com/wasp-lang/wasp/blob/main/web/versioned_docs/version-0.13.0/tutorial/07-auth.md#2025-04-22_snippet_12

LANGUAGE: javascript
