TITLE: Implementing a React Component with Wasp Query Integration
DESCRIPTION: This TypeScript React component implements the HomePage that displays the user's recipes. It uses Wasp's useQuery hook to fetch data with automatic loading state management and full-stack type safety.
SOURCE: https://github.com/wasp-lang/wasp/blob/main/web/versioned_docs/version-0.12.0/introduction/introduction.md#2025-04-22_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: tsx
