TITLE: Example Telemetry Payload for Wasp CLI Command Invocation (JSON)
DESCRIPTION: Shows the JSON structure of the anonymized telemetry data sent via HTTPS when a `wasp` CLI command is invoked. This includes a unique user ID, project hash, build status, limited deployment arguments, Wasp version, OS, and execution context (like CI). Data is sent at most twice per 12-hour period.
