TITLE: Defining Authentication Entities
DESCRIPTION: Definition of User and SocialLogin entities required for Google authentication, including their relationships and fields.
SOURCE: https://github.com/wasp-lang/wasp/blob/main/web/versioned_docs/version-0.11.8/auth/social-auth/google.md#2025-04-22_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: wasp
CODE:
```
entity User {=psl
    id          Int     @id @default(autoincrement())
    externalAuthAssociations  SocialLogin[]
psl=}

entity SocialLogin {=psl
  id          Int       @id @default(autoincrement())
  provider    String
  providerId  String
  user        User      @relation(fields: [userId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)
  userId      Int
  createdAt   DateTime  @default(now())
  @@unique([provider, providerId, userId])
psl=}
```

