TITLE: Implementing onBeforeOAuthRedirect Hook in JavaScript and TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: This hook runs before redirecting to an OAuth provider. It receives url, oauth, prisma, and req as input parameters, and must return an object with a url property that Wasp will use for the redirect.
SOURCE: https://github.com/wasp-lang/wasp/blob/main/web/versioned_docs/version-0.16.0/auth/auth-hooks.md#2025-04-22_snippet_11

LANGUAGE: JavaScript
CODE:
```
