TITLE: Basic Wasp CLI Command Structure and Options
DESCRIPTION: Overview of main Wasp CLI commands showing general usage pattern, available commands grouped by category, and common examples.
SOURCE: https://github.com/wasp-lang/wasp/blob/main/web/versioned_docs/version-0.15.0/general/cli.md#2025-04-22_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: bash
