TITLE: Enforcing Authentication in Task Query - Wasp Server (JavaScript)
DESCRIPTION: This snippet defines an authenticated query function to fetch only the tasks belonging to the currently logged-in user. It uses Wasp's HttpError for error handling and ensures only authenticated users retrieve their own tasks ordered by ID. Requires 'wasp/server' for HttpError and appropriate Prisma user-task relationships.
