TITLE: Defining Scheduled Jobs in Wasp DSL
DESCRIPTION: This Wasp code defines two scheduled background jobs: one that fetches GitHub statistics every 10 minutes and another that calculates webpage load time every 5 minutes. The jobs use PgBoss as the executor and reference worker functions from imported JavaScript modules.
